title: The Life of a Female Knight and a Dark Elf - Novel Updates
genre: Ecchi   Fantasy   Gender Bender   Shoujo Ai   Slice of Life
tags: Cooking   Elves   Female Protagonist   Knights   Male to Female   Multiple Reincarnated Individuals   Reincarnated in Another World
author: Kiriya Kadzuki   霧矢風月
description:
Kouta, a high school boy who was a victim of an unfortunate plane crash is reincarnated in another world as Schenna Urablatt.

Kouta who was reborn as a woman has to overcome many ordeals and ends up meeting his best friend in the country of Priden, who had also been victim in the plane crash, however Yasuhiro was no longer a human, he had been reincarnated as a female dark elf!

As they meet each other, the story calmly begins.>
